{"title":"求一元二次方程的根","uid":"a6d0295cac50a3997d1f089ffd724d3f","slug":"求一元二次方程的根","date":"2022-03-24T15:51:28.451Z","updated":"2022-03-24T15:51:28.451Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/求一元二次方程的根.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2022/03/6959183d55c4ac26.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"求一元二次方程的根\"><a href=\"#求一元二次方程的根\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"求一元二次方程的根\"></a>求一元二次方程的根</h2><h4 id=\"描述\"><a href=\"#描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"描述\"></a>描述</h4><p>利用公式x1 &#x3D; (-b + sqrt(b<em>b-4</em>a<em>c))&#x2F;(2</em>a), x2 &#x3D; (-b - sqrt(b<em>b-4</em>a<em>c))&#x2F;(2</em>a)求一元二次方程ax2+ bx + c &#x3D;0的根，其中a不等于0。</p>\n<h4 id=\"输入\"><a href=\"#输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入\"></a>输入</h4><p>输入一行，包含三个浮点数a, b, c（它们之间以一个空格分开），分别表示方程ax2 + bx + c &#x3D;0的系数。</p>\n<h4 id=\"输出\"><a href=\"#输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出\"></a>输出</h4><p>输出一行，表示方程的解。<br>若b2 &#x3D; 4 * a * c,则两个实根相等，则输出形式为：x1&#x3D;x2&#x3D;…；<br>若b2 &gt; 4 * a * c,则两个实根不等，则输出形式为：x1&#x3D;…;x2 &#x3D; …，其中x1&gt;x2；<br>若b2 &lt; 4 * a * c，则有两个虚根，则输出：x1&#x3D;实部+虚部i; x2&#x3D;实部-虚部i，即x1的虚部系数大于等于x2的虚部系数，实部为0时不可省略。实部 &#x3D; -b &#x2F; (2<em>a)，虚部 &#x3D; sqrt(4</em>a<em>c-b</em>b) &#x2F; (2*a)</p>\n<p>所有实数部分要求精确到小数点后5位，数字、符号之间没有空格。</p>\n<h4 id=\"样例输入\"><a href=\"#样例输入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输入\"></a>样例输入</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">样例输入1\n1.0  2.0  8.0\n\n样例输入2\n1  0  1</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输出\"><a href=\"#样例输出\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输出\"></a>样例输出</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">样例输出1\nx1&#x3D;-1.00000+2.64575i;x2&#x3D;-1.00000-2.64575i\n\n样例输出2\nx1&#x3D;0.00000+1.00000i;x2&#x3D;0.00000-1.00000i</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"思路\"><a href=\"#思路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"思路\"></a>思路</h4><p>见解答</p>\n<h4 id=\"解答\"><a href=\"#解答\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解答\"></a>解答</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;iostream&gt;\n#include &lt;cstdio&gt;\n#include &lt;math.h&gt;\n\nusing namespace std;\n\nint main()\n&#123;\n    float a, b, c, x1, x2, x, real, imag;\n    scanf(&quot;%f%f%f&quot;, &amp;a, &amp;b, &amp;c);\n    if (b*b &gt; 4*a*c)&#123;\n    \tx1 &#x3D; (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c)) &#x2F; (2*a);\n   \t\tx2 &#x3D; (-b - sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c)) &#x2F; (2*a);\n   \t\tprintf(&quot;x1&#x3D;%.5f;x2&#x3D;%.5f&quot;, x1, x2);\n\t&#125;\n\telse if (b*b &#x3D;&#x3D; 4*a*c)&#123;\n\t\tx &#x3D; (-b + sqrt(b*b - 4*a*c)) &#x2F; (2*a);\n\t\tprintf(&quot;x1&#x3D;x2&#x3D;%.5f&quot;, x);\n\t&#125;\n\telse if (b*b &lt; 4*a*c)&#123;\n\t\tif (b &#x3D;&#x3D; 0)\n\t\t\treal &#x3D; 0.0;\n\t\telse real &#x3D; -b &#x2F; (2*a);\n\t\timag &#x3D; sqrt(4*a*c - b*b) &#x2F; (2*a);\n\t\tprintf(&quot;x1&#x3D;%.5f+%.5fi;x2&#x3D;%.5f-%.5fi&quot;, real, imag, real, imag);\n\t&#125;\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n","text":"求一元二次方程的根描述利用公式x1 &#x3D; (-b + sqrt(bb-4ac))&#x2F;(2a), x2 &#x3D; (-b - sqrt(bb-4ac))&#x2F;(2a)求一元二次方程ax2+ bx + c &#x3D;0的根，其中a不等于0。 输入输入一行，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":12,"path":"api/categories/C.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":12,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"OpenJudge","slug":"OpenJudge","count":12,"path":"api/tags/OpenJudge.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%80%E5%85%83%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">求一元二次方程的根</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">输出</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-it